<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head><%- include('../partials/head') %></head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="container" style="padding-top:48px;padding-bottom:60px">

    <!-- Hero About -->
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px">
      <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:#FFF4E0;color:#C47D10;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:16px">✦ Tentang Kami</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:12px">Platform Kurban Digital<br><span style="color:var(--primary)">Terpercaya di Indonesia</span></h1>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto">QurbanIn menghadirkan pengalaman berqurban yang modern, transparan, dan bermakna — sambil mendukung peternak lokal di seluruh Indonesia.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Row -->
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:48px">
      <div class="card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:4px">120+</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500">Hewan Tersedia</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:4px">30+</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500">Peternak Mitra</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:28px;text-align:center">
        <div style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:4px">500+</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500">Pembeli Puas</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Visi Misi -->
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-bottom:48px">
      <div class="card" style="padding:32px">
        <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--primary-light);border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:16px">🎯</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px">Visi Kami</h2>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75">Membuat proses qurban lebih transparan, mudah diakses, dan relevan dengan gaya hidup digital masa kini — sehingga setiap orang bisa berqurban dengan tenang dan keyakinan penuh.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:32px">
        <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:#FFF4E0;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:16px">🚀</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px">Misi Kami</h2>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px">
            <span style="width:20px;height:20px;background:var(--primary-light);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px">1</span>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6">Mendukung peternak lokal dengan akses pasar yang lebih luas.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px">
            <span style="width:20px;height:20px;background:var(--primary-light);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px">2</span>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6">Memudahkan masyarakat beribadah dengan cara yang praktis dan aman.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px">
            <span style="width:20px;height:20px;background:var(--primary-light);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px">3</span>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6">Menyediakan hewan qurban berkualitas sesuai syariat.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Nilai Kami -->
    <div style="margin-bottom:48px">
      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:20px">Nilai yang Kami Pegang</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px">
        <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
          <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:12px">🤝</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">Kepercayaan</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6">Setiap transaksi dijamin transparan dan dapat dilacak oleh pembeli.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
          <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:12px">🌿</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">Keberkahan</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6">Setiap hewan dipastikan sehat dan memenuhi syarat qurban sesuai syariat Islam.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
          <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:12px">💡</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">Inovasi</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6">Kami terus berinovasi agar pengalaman berqurban semakin mudah dan modern.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div style="background:#F0FAF5;border:0.5px solid var(--primary-border);border-radius:20px;padding:40px;text-align:center">
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:10px">Siap Berqurban Tahun Ini?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:24px">Temukan hewan kurban terbaik dari peternak terverifikasi kami.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center">
        <a href="/animals" class="btn-primary">Lihat Katalog →</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn-outline">Daftar Sekarang</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>